159
00:11:33,150 --> 00:11:34,150
Saya harus pergi.

160
00:11:34,193 --> 00:11:35,433
Apakah kamu menghindariku karena…

161
00:11:37,154 --> 00:11:38,356
Biarkan aku lewat.

162
00:11:40,032 --> 00:11:41,033
Aku bilang, biarkan aku lewat!

163
00:11:41,351 --> 00:11:42,493
- Jay!
- Biarkan aku lewat!

164
00:11:43,160 --> 00:11:45,305
Anda perlu mengakui siapa Anda
tipe ada di antara kita semua...

165
00:11:45,329 --> 00:11:46,329
Diam!

166
00:11:46,639 --> 00:11:47,456
Kemarilah.

167
00:11:47,508 --> 00:11:48,623
- Oke.
- Pergi ke sana.

168
00:11:50,251 --> 00:11:51,419
Hentikan! Mari kita bicara.

169
00:11:51,544 --> 00:11:52,544
Oke!

170
00:11:54,588 --> 00:11:55,923
Tidak bisakah aku membisikkannya padamu saja?

171
00:11:56,674 --> 00:11:58,434
- Aku akan membisikkannya padamu.
- Kesepakatan tetaplah kesepakatan.

172
00:11:58,564 --> 00:11:59,634
